  * Improve test suite:
    + Fix compatibility with Python 3.X (broken in 0.3.5).
    + Test expression parsing again.
    + Capture stderr output for tests which produce unhandled exceptions.
  * Fix compatibility with Python 2.5 (broken since 0.3.0).

